What is Smart Anesthesia Robot?
Smart Anesthesia Robot is an advanced robotic system that automates the delivery of anesthetic agents during surgical procedures. It operates as a closed‑loop drug delivery platform, continuously assessing physiological parameters such as Bispectral Index (BIS), heart rate, blood pressure, and oxygen saturation to adjust infusion rates in real time. By integrating real‑time data from a variety of sensors, the robot ensures that anesthetic depth is maintained within a target range, thereby enhancing patient safety and procedural consistency.
